# End-to-End DevSecOps, GitOps & Observability Platform Documentation

## Project Objective

Build a production-style DevSecOps platform capable of:

* Building and validating microservices
* Security scanning throughout the CI pipeline
* Container image creation and distribution
* Automated Kubernetes deployments
* GitOps-driven delivery
* Metrics monitoring and visualization
* Centralized log aggregation and analysis

